305
00:17:24,609 --> 00:17:25,200
Saya merayu awak.

306
00:17:25,201 --> 00:17:26,260
Tidak.

307
00:17:27,320 --> 00:17:28,490
Taiga-senpai...

308
00:17:28,590 --> 00:17:31,260
Pergi. Jika anda kalah, anda berada dalam beg tidur.

309
00:17:32,340 --> 00:17:33,820
Adakah anda mahu Sara berasa tidak selesa?

310
00:17:34,490 --> 00:17:35,490
Kita tidak boleh memilikinya, bukan? Betul ke?

311
